HEADWORD: Plantership
<hw>Plant"er*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The occupation or position of
a planter, or the management of a plantation, as in the United States or
the West Indies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

